Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:15.54,Opening,,0,0,0,,My right hand holds a bowl of gold,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.54,0:00:19.79,Opening,,0,0,0,,And my left holds one of silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.79,0:00:24.46,Opening,,0,0,0,,Never one without the other,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:37.70,Opening,,0,0,0,,Two unseen bowls for each of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.70,0:00:45.98,Opening,,0,0,0,,The golden one is filled with joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:53.45,Opening,,0,0,0,,shining warmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.45,0:00:57.99,Opening,,0,0,0,,Since we met, my golden bowl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.99,0:01:05.26,Opening,,0,0,0,,cannot hold all my happiness and love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:15.40,Opening,,0,0,0,,Golden joy, silver sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.40,0:01:22.75,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would leave my past behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.75,0:01:27.48,Opening,,0,0,0,,For you, for the sake of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.48,0:01:34.42,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would empty the bowls of my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.35,0:02:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,My Dear Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.80,0:02:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaoru-no-Kimi is leaving the hospital today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.69,0:02:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Though it was only overnight, and a simple basketball injury,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.36,0:02:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It is still a special occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.97,0:02:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's taking so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.10,0:02:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,In attendance are Mariko-san and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.37,0:02:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama is not present.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.11,0:02:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.52,0:02:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.32,0:02:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations on your discharge!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.26,0:02:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! You came to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.93,0:02:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.20,0:02:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations on your discharge!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.26,0:02:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.53,0:02:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But isn't this a bit much?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.78,0:02:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I was only in the hospital for observation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.61,0:02:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But I couldn't sleep all night for worrying!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:02:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.32,0:03:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh I see! My worrying isn't important enough to concern you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.53,0:03:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.15,0:03:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, these are some of my favorite flowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.60,0:03:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you... Mariko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.69,0:03:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You made me so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.29,0:03:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.03,0:03:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.43,0:03:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the first time you used my first name!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.77,0:03:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.51,0:03:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at Mariko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.61,0:03:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,17. Post Scriptum
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.06,0:03:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So she's already out of the hospital? Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.83,0:03:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad it wasn't serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.64,0:03:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, and starting tomorrow she can even exercise a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.59,0:04:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But what a surprise! The way Mariko-san adores Kaoru-no-Kimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.54,0:04:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.52,0:04:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither did I!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.56,0:04:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.41,0:04:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true, my dear Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.15,0:04:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know when Mariko began to adore Kaoru-no-Kimi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.96,0:04:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is love. Real love.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.10,0:04:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She's so honest and direct with her feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.67,0:04:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko-san just can't lie to herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.17,0:04:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes sense, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.51,0:04:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.30,0:04:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaoru-no-Kimi is more manly than the pathetic boys around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.38,0:04:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...and so good-looking!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.45,0:04:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And that way she talks: effervescent, like fresh soda!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So Mariko-san got to her first!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.12,0:04:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.23,0:04:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Mariko-san who got her...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.33,0:04:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.06,0:05:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm kidding! Let's just say I'm kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.54,0:05:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt envious of her, my Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko-san is so direct...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.28,0:05:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come to like Mariko-san very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.37,0:05:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.92,0:06:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.79,0:06:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father wants to talk to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.06,0:06:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok! I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.20,0:06:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.13,0:06:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.40,0:06:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear Brother, when I compare myself to Mariko,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.21,0:06:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't be as frank as she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.57,0:06:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still sore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.26,0:07:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Get in. I'll take you to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.12,0:07:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You played in the basketball game?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.80,0:07:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.74,0:07:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what should I think of all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.54,0:07:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you enjoy it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.75,0:07:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.81,0:07:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd really like to know, so I'll ask you again...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.35,0:07:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yes. I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.60,0:07:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.49,0:07:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.83,0:07:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.83,0:07:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me ask you once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.70,0:07:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you enjoy it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.17,0:07:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No. They made me play. I had to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.91,0:08:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? That's better, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.98,0:08:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let go of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.85,0:08:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You must never forget...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.99,0:08:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,...that there is no one who understands you better than I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.33,0:08:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.93,0:08:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.42,0:08:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.16,0:08:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.66,0:08:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.10,0:09:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. They only affect you. No one else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.04,0:09:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But think of yourself for once. And you'll see you shouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.91,0:09:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What did Miya-sama say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.23,0:09:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You came here together, right? I saw you getting out of her car.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.32,0:09:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand them over!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.93,0:09:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it! Hand them over!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.67,0:09:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, that basketball game...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.81,0:09:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...I had a great time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.35,0:09:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You make me proud, Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaoru-no-Kimi... ...won't you have lunch with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.37,0:10:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I really should check in with the Coach first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.67,0:10:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, we need to go over the schedule for the city tournaments...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.52,0:10:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.85,0:10:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.76,0:10:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.81,0:10:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.13,0:10:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.54,0:10:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,She's as popular as ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.15,0:10:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It happened suddenly, my Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.62,0:11:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart began to race.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.78,0:11:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt flushed and hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.76,0:11:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I wasn't sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.43,0:11:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...there seemed to be tears in my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.84,0:11:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.77,0:11:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry! Tomoko might be looking for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.39,0:11:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.73,0:11:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Mix lightly, put it into a lightly buttered and powdered pan...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.49,0:11:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,...then put it into the oven at 180, wait for fifteen minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.25,0:11:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,...and it will turn light brown. Then it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.87,0:11:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you're asking me all this, are you planning on baking something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.17,0:11:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... I'm planning on it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.19,0:11:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm, hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.92,0:11:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Heartwarming, homemade cookies!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.46,0:11:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone would love getting cookies, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.40,0:11:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.53,0:11:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh... I wish I could just give her my soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.87,0:11:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Whatever you say!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.73,0:11:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I just remembered...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.47,0:11:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I have an errand to run at the student store...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.54,0:11:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.36,0:11:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.08,0:11:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.75,0:12:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. We just sold our last stamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.82,0:12:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.38,0:12:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Look at these flowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.31,0:12:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.61,0:13:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.12,0:13:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.52,0:13:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What is she thinking? What is she feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.47,0:13:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.76,0:13:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She's all alone in the gym, in the early afternoon...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.60,0:13:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,...it can only be that she is love-sick for someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.60,0:13:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.60,0:14:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Upsetting a pretty girl like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.77,0:14:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Orihara Kaoru should be ashamed of herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.01,0:14:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like that! That's not it at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.55,0:14:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.72,0:14:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,For goodness sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.19,0:14:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaoru-no-Kimi is for Mariko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.06,0:14:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.49,0:15:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,My Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.56,0:15:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I have misplaced a very important letter to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.64,0:15:45.11,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,...written in plain English, the book is suitable for beginners.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.11,0:15:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how it goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.47,0:15:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Kusunoki-sensei, I have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.73,0:15:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Miss Shinobu, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.73,0:15:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If one omitted the word {\i1}"being"{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.12,0:15:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,...would the adverb clause go from passive voice to active voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.27,0:16:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a good question, Miss Shinobu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.06,0:16:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Look how alive Mariko-san is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.19,0:16:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,She is overflowing with self-confidence,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.73,0:16:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,...and seems so much more positive than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.93,0:16:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Her beauty has even become more refined...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.14,0:16:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...and Love has given her a new allure...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.81,0:16:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But unlike Mariko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.23,0:16:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...I just feel confused, my Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.41,0:16:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Bringing it to school was a mistake...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.79,0:16:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I could have bought a stamp near home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.13,0:16:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, at the next break I'll take care of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.15,0:16:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, bell!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.96,0:16:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.60,0:17:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did I lose it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.30,0:17:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.34,0:17:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A lost letter? Nobody's brought one to the student office.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.47,0:17:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.20,0:17:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.64,0:17:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What? A letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.47,0:17:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going to mail it at lunch time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What'll I do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.69,0:17:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.84,0:17:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me it's a letter to a boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.95,0:17:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako-san! Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.49,0:17:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,A boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.12,0:17:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.76,0:17:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.51,0:17:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.73,0:17:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I forbid it! You cannot date a boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.64,0:17:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It... it's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.26,0:17:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't! No way! Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.70,0:17:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You just don't know how men are!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.24,0:18:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They're dirty, disgusting, shameless, selfish, and abusive!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.93,0:18:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.94,0:18:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If they look gentle it's a only a front!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.72,0:18:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Only an illusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.90,0:18:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So, don't! Don't date any men! I forbid it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.37,0:18:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.32,0:18:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't! Don't do it! Don't! Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.36,0:18:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.25,0:18:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So, let's go. 6th period is starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.89,0:18:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.01,0:18:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give up looking for my letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.14,0:18:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give up on it. That's what I told myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.05,0:18:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't like the thought that someone might find it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.87,0:18:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...and peek into our relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.09,0:18:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But it shouldn't cause any problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.31,0:18:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There wasn't anything I wrote that would cause a problem for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.73,0:18:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.73,0:19:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Misonoo-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.73,0:19:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.89,0:19:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Mona-Lisa-sama? Borgia-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.05,0:19:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukiko-sama has something important to discuss with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.51,0:19:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,W-With me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.74,0:19:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Misonoo-san, with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.06,0:19:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to her house after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.98,0:19:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.11,0:19:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you know already.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.27,0:19:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Miya-sama likes you, so don't make trouble for her...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.20,0:19:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.97,0:19:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we made ourselves clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.67,0:19:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you do something to upset Miya-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.15,0:19:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.03,0:20:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What if!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.83,0:20:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I was hoping my premonition would not be true...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.94,0:20:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How was that? That serenade was for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.77,0:20:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What? For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.54,0:21:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It was wonderful! Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.21,0:21:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad it appealed to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.80,0:21:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you be so kind as to make tea for me too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.75,0:21:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.57,0:21:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't take sugar, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.10,0:21:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.71,0:21:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.55,0:21:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.50,0:21:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Henmi Takehiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.19,0:21:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me, but I saw to whom it was addressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.93,0:21:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.66,0:21:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But, thank goodness, it was a Sorority member who found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.58,0:21:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If it had been found by someone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.29,0:22:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,...it would have started rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.09,0:22:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.05,0:22:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're nothing but apologies!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.04,0:22:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.93,0:22:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I ask you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.73,0:22:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...not to date any boys?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.68,0:22:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.39,0:22:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's a pen-pal! Just a pen-pal!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.42,0:22:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, perhaps that is so...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.24,0:22:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...but how can you guarantee that a romance won't follow?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.60,0:22:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I like your gentle nature...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.46,0:22:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...and how obedient and submissive you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.48,0:22:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Now... tear it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.56,0:22:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.88,0:22:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Right in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.01,0:23:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.81,0:23:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,My Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.24,0:23:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.92,0:23:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I just wanted to tease you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.30,0:23:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.74,0:23:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.35,0:23:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to drop this in a mailbox right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.75,0:23:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart travels along with this letter,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.53,0:23:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...so please read this a bit more carefully than past letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.50,0:23:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the letter that was lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.64,0:23:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,P.S. from she whose heart beats faster around a certain someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.73,0:23:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,...and from the one who has been a little strange lately...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.06,0:24:14.26,Ending,,0,0,0,,I dreamed I was chasing a rainbow...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.26,0:24:19.73,Ending,,0,0,0,,Then the rainbow I was chasing was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.20,0:24:25.34,Ending,,0,0,0,,Before, I had no strength, no will.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.34,0:24:30.81,Ending,,0,0,0,,But now because of you, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.55,0:24:37.09,Ending,,0,0,0,,Feelings of love, like raindrops
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.09,0:24:42.56,Ending,,0,0,0,,Come pouring from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.56,0:24:45.29,Ending,,0,0,0,,This is surely a game
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.29,0:24:48.10,Ending,,0,0,0,,Of some mischievous fairy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.10,0:24:50.50,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always dancing,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.50,0:24:55.77,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always capricious...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.19,0:25:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako and Saint-Juste skip class and go to the park,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.19,0:25:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...where they encounter Henmi and Takashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.09,0:25:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste calls Takashi her "brother"...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.75,0:25:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako finally confesses her feelings to Saint-Juste.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.70,0:25:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Next episode: Into the Dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.81,0:25:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, Dear Brother... There is no end to my tears...
